</div></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">授業計画</div><div style="margin:10px"><p>This course will focus on positive psychology. You will use the textbook GOAL and additional materials supplied by the teacher.</p>
<p>If this course is taught in hybrid format, then students will do the GOAL textbook in class and the positive psychology materials in on-demand format, alternating each week.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Week 1. Dream</p>
<p>Week 2. Wheel of Life</p>
<p>Week 3. Set Clear Goals</p>
<p>Week 4. Take Action</p>
<p>Week 5. Learn From Failute</p>
<p>Week 6. The Inner Game</p>
<p>Week 7. The Outer Game</p>
<p>Week 8-14: Themes from Positive Psychology including</p>
<p> - Positive Emotion</p>
<p> - Engagement</p>
<p> - Relationships</p>
<p> - Meaning</p>
<p> - Achievement</p>
<p>Week 15: Final Test</p></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">成績評価の方法</div><div style="margin:10px"><p>Students will be required to understand the material and to use the tools of positive psychology and goalsetting in their own lives. </p></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">成績評価の基準</div><div style="margin:10px">秀　 達成目標を超えた成果を上げている　100点～90点<br>優　 達成目標に十分達している　　　　　89点～80点<br>良　 達成目標に達している　　　　　　　79点～70点<br>可　 達成目標に概ね達している　　　　　69点～60点<br>不可 達成目標に達していない　　　　　　59点以下<br><p>Moodle Work: 40%</p>
<p>Classwork: 40%</p>
<p>Final Assignment: 20%</p>
<p> </p></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">事前・事後学修等の指示及び履修にあたっての注意事項</div><div style="margin:10px"><p>You must take part actively in all Moodle and classroom activities</p>
<p align="left">事前学修：教科書や教材の予習，予習課題に取り組む。 （120 分）</p>
<p align="left">事後学修：授業内の講義や解説を理解し，事後課題（レポート，プレゼンテーション，小テストなど）に取り組む。（120分）</p></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">教科書</div><div style="margin:10px"><a href="http://opac.lib.nitech.ac.jp/opc/recordID/catalog.bib/NB02228213" target=_blank>GOAL: Identify and Achieve Your Life Goals<a><br></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">参考書</div><div style="margin:10px"></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">オフィスアワー</div><div style="margin:10px"><p>First, contact me by message on Moodle. </p>
